{"tha-ap489:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap489:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap489:0.3":"7 Pulinuppadakattheraapadana ","tha-ap489:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap489:1.2":"devalo nama tapaso; ","tha-ap489:1.3":"Tattha me cankamo asi, ","tha-ap489:1.4":"amanussehi mapito. ","tha-ap489:2.1":"Jatabharena bharito, ","tha-ap489:2.2":"kamandaludharo sada; ","tha-ap489:2.3":"Uttamattham gavesanto, ","tha-ap489:2.4":"vipina nikkhamim tada. ","tha-ap489:3.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap489:3.2":"sissa mayham upatthahum; ","tha-ap489:3.3":"Sakakammabhipasuta, ","tha-ap489:3.4":"vasanti vipine tada. ","tha-ap489:4.1":"Assama abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap489:4.2":"akam pulinacetiyam; ","tha-ap489:4.3":"Nanapuppham samanetva, ","tha-ap489:4.4":"tam cetiyamapujayim. ","tha-ap489:5.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap489:5.2":"assamam pavisamaham; ","tha-ap489:5.3":"Sabbe sissa samagantva, ","tha-ap489:5.4":"etamattham pucchimsu mam. ","tha-ap489:6.1":"‘Pulinena kato thupo, ","tha-ap489:6.2":"yam tvam deva namassasi; ","tha-ap489:6.3":"Mayampi natumicchama, ","tha-ap489:6.4":"puttho acikkha no tuvam’. ","tha-ap489:7.1":"‘Niddittha nu mantapade, ","tha-ap489:7.2":"cakkhumanto mahayasa; ","tha-ap489:7.3":"Te kho aham namassami, ","tha-ap489:7.4":"buddhasetthe mahayase. ","tha-ap489:8.1":"Kidisa te mahavira, ","tha-ap489:8.2":"sabbannu lokanayaka; ","tha-ap489:8.3":"Kathamvanna kathamsila, ","tha-ap489:8.4":"kidisa te mahayasa. ","tha-ap489:9.1":"Battimsalakkhana buddha, ","tha-ap489:9.2":"cattalisadijapi ca; ","tha-ap489:9.3":"Netta gopakhuma tesam, ","tha-ap489:9.4":"jinjuka phalasannibha. ","tha-ap489:10.1":"Gacchamana ca te buddha, ","tha-ap489:10.2":"yugamattanca pekkhare; ","tha-ap489:10.3":"Na tesam janu nadati, ","tha-ap489:10.4":"sandhisaddo na suyyati. ","tha-ap489:11.1":"Gacchamana ca sugata, ","tha-ap489:11.2":"uddharantava gacchare; ","tha-ap489:11.3":"Pathamam dakkhinam padam, ","tha-ap489:11.4":"buddhanam esa dhammata. ","tha-ap489:12.1":"Asambhita ca te buddha, ","tha-ap489:12.2":"migarajava kesari; ","tha-ap489:12.3":"Nevukkamsenti attanam, ","tha-ap489:12.4":"no ca vambhenti paninam. ","tha-ap489:13.1":"Manavamanato mutta, ","tha-ap489:13.2":"sama sabbesu panisu; ","tha-ap489:13.3":"Anattukkamsaka buddha, ","tha-ap489:13.4":"buddhanam esa dhammata. ","tha-ap489:14.1":"Uppajjanta ca sambuddha, ","tha-ap489:14.2":"alokam dassayanti te; ","tha-ap489:14.3":"Chappakaram pakampenti, ","tha-ap489:14.4":"kevalam vasudham imam. ","tha-ap489:15.1":"Passanti nirayancete, ","tha-ap489:15.2":"nibbati nirayo tada; ","tha-ap489:15.3":"Pavassati mahamegho, ","tha-ap489:15.4":"buddhanam esa dhammata. ","tha-ap489:16.1":"Idisa te mahanaga, ","tha-ap489:16.2":"atula ca mahayasa; ","tha-ap489:16.3":"Vannato anatikkanta, ","tha-ap489:16.4":"appameyya tathagata’. ","tha-ap489:17.1":"Anumodimsu me vakyam, ","tha-ap489:17.2":"sabbe sissa sagarava; ","tha-ap489:17.3":"Tatha ca patipajjimsu, ","tha-ap489:17.4":"yathasatti yathabalam. ","tha-ap489:18.1":"Patipujenti pulinam, ","tha-ap489:18.2":"sakakammabhilasino; ","tha-ap489:18.3":"Saddahanta mama vakyam, ","tha-ap489:18.4":"buddhasakkatamanasa. ","tha-ap489:19.1":"Tada cavitva tusita, ","tha-ap489:19.2":"devaputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap489:19.3":"Uppajji matukucchimhi, ","tha-ap489:19.4":"dasasahassi kampatha. ","tha-ap489:20.1":"Assamassaviduramhi, ","tha-ap489:20.2":"cankamamhi thito aham; ","tha-ap489:20.3":"Sabbe sissa samagantva, ","tha-ap489:20.4":"agacchum mama santike. ","tha-ap489:21.1":"‘Usabhova mahi nadati, ","tha-ap489:21.2":"migarajava kujati; ","tha-ap489:21.3":"Susumarova salati, ","tha-ap489:21.4":"kim vipako bhavissati’. ","tha-ap489:22.1":"‘Yam pakittemi sambuddham, ","tha-ap489:22.2":"sikatathupasantike; ","tha-ap489:22.3":"So dani bhagava sattha, ","tha-ap489:22.4":"matukucchimupagami’. ","tha-ap489:23.1":"Tesam dhammakatham vatva, ","tha-ap489:23.2":"kittayitva mahamunim; ","tha-ap489:23.3":"Uyyojetva sake sisse, ","tha-ap489:23.4":"pallankamabhujim aham. ","tha-ap489:24.1":"Balanca vata me khinam, ","tha-ap489:24.2":"byadhina paramena tam; ","tha-ap489:24.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap489:24.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap489:25.1":"Sabbe sissa samagantva, ","tha-ap489:25.2":"akamsu citakam tada; ","tha-ap489:25.3":"Kalevaranca me gayha, ","tha-ap489:25.4":"citakam abhiropayum. ","tha-ap489:26.1":"Citakam parivaretva, ","tha-ap489:26.2":"sise katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap489:26.3":"Sokasallapareta te, ","tha-ap489:26.4":"vikkandimsu samagata. ","tha-ap489:27.1":"Tesam lalappamananam, ","tha-ap489:27.2":"agamam citakam tada; ","tha-ap489:27.3":"‘Aham acariyo tumham, ","tha-ap489:27.4":"ma socittha sumedhasa. ","tha-ap489:28.1":"Sadatthe vayameyyatha, ","tha-ap489:28.2":"rattindivamatandita; ","tha-ap489:28.3":"Ma vo pamatta ahuttha, ","tha-ap489:28.4":"khano vo patipadito’. ","tha-ap489:29.1":"Sake sissenusasitva, ","tha-ap489:29.2":"devalokam punagamim; ","tha-ap489:29.3":"Attharasa ca kappani, ","tha-ap489:29.4":"devaloke ramamaham. ","tha-ap489:30.1":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap489:30.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap489:30.3":"Anekasatakkhattunca, ","tha-ap489:30.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap489:31.1":"Avasesesu kappesu, ","tha-ap489:31.2":"vokinno samsarim aham; ","tha-ap489:31.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap489:31.4":"uppadassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap489:32.1":"Yatha komudike mase, ","tha-ap489:32.2":"bahu pupphanti padapa; ","tha-ap489:32.3":"Tathevahampi samaye, ","tha-ap489:32.4":"pupphitomhi mahesina. ","tha-ap489:33.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","tha-ap489:33.2":"yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","tha-ap489:33.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap489:33.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap489:34.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap489:34.2":"yam buddhamabhikittayim; ","tha-ap489:34.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap489:34.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap489:35.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap489:35.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap489:35.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap489:36.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap489:36.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap489:36.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap489:37.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap489:37.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap489:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap489:38.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pulinuppadako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap489:39.1":"Pulinuppadakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}